main_body:
Every application for the right to import lodged in accordance with Regulation (EC) No 1143/98 shall be granted to the following extent:
(a) for importers covered by Article 2(1)(a) of Regulation (EC) No 1143/98, 51,7282 % of the quantities imported during the period 1 July 2000 to 30 June 2003;
(b) for importers covered by Article 2(1)(b) of Regulation (EC) No 1143/98, 6,8393 % of the quantities applied for.
